						<div class="postbody">I'd like to try and learn how to make the nes stretch out a bg image. I've seen it done vertically to an image, I've also seen a wavy bg effect, really neat. But I have no clue as to how to start trying this on my own, what addresses to mess with, etc. Could I get some pointers/suggestions? Thanks!</div>

