				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">These effect usualy involve writting to PPU adresses, $2006 and $2007. Sometimes you might want to also use $2005.<br />In my game, <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oSHa9icHOwk" class="postlink">FamiDepth</a>, wavy title screen is achieved by timed writes during <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Horizontal_blanking_interval" class="postlink">hblank</a> to said registers.<br />Keep in mind this kind of effects tend to hog the cpu....so it isn't used during gameplay very often.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

