					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">oh, Tokumaru is right, I dont know why I said $2007, haha.<br />When hblank starts, the ppu updates <em>t</em> horizontal component of scrolling.<br />In FamiDepth, I change x position by writing to $2005 every scanline afterwhich I wait for a scanline to pass.<br />During cycle burning, I read $2002 to reset the write toggle.</div>

