				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The main &quot;catch&quot; is that mid-screen vertical scroll changes via $2005 don't work. The vertical scroll will NOT change on the second write to $2005, so you have to use a more elaborate sequence of $2006/5/5/6 writes to fully set the X and Y scroll mid-screen.</div>

